                                    <p>P. M.</p>
                                    <p>5.—Sounded off Point Roberts, 50 fathoms.</p>
                                    <p>5.30.—Eased, stopped and came to with B. B. in 11 fathoms.
                                        Veered to 48 fathoms. Banked up fires. Point Roberts, S. 55°
                                        E. South Point Fraser’s River, N. 48° W.</p>
